data.description: Welcome to your charming retreat nestled in the heart of Glenmora. This enchanting 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom cottage style home exudes warmth and character at every turn.Step inside and be greeted by the cozy ambiance and inviting open floor plan that fills the space with natural light, creating a perfect spot for relaxing or entertaining guests.The heart of the home lies in the well-appointed kitchen, where modern conveniences blend seamlessly with rustic charm. Tucked away in the cul de sac of a developing subdivision that offers the perfect balance of tranquility and accessibility. Don't miss your chance to own this gem of a property and make cherished memories for years to come.
